2008 album from the cosmic band, the follow-up to the multi platinum selling albums Tired Of Hanging Around and the Nationwide Mercury Prize nominated debut Who Killed The Zutons? You Can Do Anything was recorded at Sunset Sound Studios in LA during January/February 2008 and was produced by George Drakoulias (The Black Crowes/Primal Scream/Tom Petty). 12 tracks including the single &#039;Always Right Behind You&#039;.
